The mirror is now attributed to an excavation in **Tsuchida, [[:en:Kani, Gifu|Kani, Gifu]], Gifu Prefecture**, and is **from the same mold as mirrors discovered at**: - **[[:en:Nishimotomezuka Kofun|Saikumezuka Kofun]]** (Hyōgo Prefecture) - **[[:en:Tsubai Ōtsukayama Kofun|Tsubai Ōtsukayama Kofun]]** (Kyoto Prefecture) - **{{ill|Shiroyama No.1 Kofun (Katori, Chiba)|ja|城山1号墳 (香取市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiroyama No.1 Kofun (Katori, Chiba)|qq=}}** (Chiba Prefecture)
